/*增加hello_drive*/
../linux-2.6.32.2/drivers/char 目錄下
1.增加 hello.c
2.Kconfig 增加
----------------------------------------------------------------
config Hello_word_MINI2440
	tristate "test Support for Mini2440 hello"
	depends on MACH_MINI2440
	default y if MACH_MINI2440
	help
	  This option enables support for Hello word on Mini2440 boards.
----------------------------------------------------------------
3.Makefile 增加obj-$(CONFIG_Hello_word_MINI2440) += hello.o

4.make menuconfig
-->DeviceDrivers -->Character devices-->[＊]test Support for Mini2440 hello
＊直接安裝進入default module
M 生成module.ko 檔（可透過insmod安裝）

5.make zImage  (make module)
